question: How many military veterans have been seen by healthcare from the 1st of January 2024 and referred to a suitable Military Veterans pathway?
sql:
SELECT HcpPatients.Id, HcpPatients.Forename, HcpPatients.Surname, HcpPatients.Gender, Maintenance_ArmedForcesType.Name
FROM   HcpPatients INNER JOIN
Maintenance_ArmedForcesType ON HcpPatients.ArmedForcesTypeId = Maintenance_ArmedForcesType.Id
where HcpPatients.ArmedForcesTypeId  in (1,2);
